description: Are you looking for the absolute best handcrafted ice cream in all of North Carolina? If the number one ice cream is what you're after, it's got to be Two Roosters Ice Cream! With the greatest tastes that North Carolina has to offer, Two Roosters is bringing a unique and amazing style to the ice cream world, and you'll be sure to agree when you have your first scoop!
name: Two Roosters Ice Cream
